p://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/pages/edit/2\" cta_title=\"JOIN RUBYSHOP\" cta_description=\"Join RUBYSHOP to register your tools and help protect your investment, rate and review products you love, and learn about the newest RUBYSHOP tools and accessories.\" cta_button_text=\"SIGN UP NOW\" cta_button_link=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/pages/edit/2\" enable_lazy_loading=\"yes\"][/rubyshop-services]</shortcode><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 'ads/rubyshop-catalog2.jpg', 'homepage', '', 'published', '2025-01-21 21:20:43', '2026-05-12 08:20:26'),
