ักษา ([www.arkcothailand.com](https://www.arkcothailand.com/news/4#:~:text=%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B4%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%A5%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%89%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%A7%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%9A%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%8A%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%82%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B7%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%9E%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B5%20Airless%20%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%94%E0%B9%89%203%20%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%9A,%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%88%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%9F%E0%B8%9F%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%B2%20%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%8A%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%20%E0%B8%9E%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%9E%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%20%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%96%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%99%20%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%97%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B7%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%95%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B3%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%94%E0%B9%89%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%A5%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%A7)).    \r\n\r\n## ข้อควรระวังในการใช้งาน    \r\nการพ่นสีเป็นงานที่เกี่ยวข้องกับสารเคมีและละอองฝุ่น ผู้ใช้งานควรระวังควรสวมชุดป้องกันส่วนบุคคล (PPE) เช่น แว่นตา หน้ากาก และถูงมือ เพื่อป้องกันอันตรายจากการสูดดมและสัมผัสกับละอองสี ([nordicban.net](https://nordicban.net/business/5-%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B8%E0%B8%9C%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%9E%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%99/#:~:text=%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%8A%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%9E%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%87%20%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%88%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%8A%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%9A%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%A5%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%A7%20%E0%B